data.description: Motivated Seller! Still time to be in your new time before Christmas!!!..........This beautiful custom-built home sits on 5 cleared acres, and is located on a quiet country road with easy access to I-75.  As you make your turn onto the property you immediately feel the peace and tranquility of country living.  As you approach the home your imagination will go to work with endless possibilities this property has to offer.  Upon entering you will instantly notice the wide open living space that creates a great home base after a tiresome day on the farm!  The home features just over 2000 square feet of living space, with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a large covered back porch with great views for that morning cup of coffee or endless entertaining.  Some of the amenities of the home include granite countertops, gorgeous solid wood cabinets, brand new kitchen appliances, very large laundry room/pantry, 2019 metal roof, 2019 AC, and tile flooring throughout except for bedrooms.  The picturesque 5 acres is fully fenced and hosts a barn/storage for your farm friends, that includes fully fenced pasture areas. The possibilities really are endless! Check out our Matterport video and get your showing booked because this priced to sell and will not last!
